nodes.text: The moons of Ai'ken Prime were a group of at least two moons located within the galaxy. Lord Hossferin of the Vandelae star system Hossferins traveled from the moons of Ai'ken Prime to visit the queen of Ktath'atn, but was killed by her lieutenant, Bombinax.
The moons of Ai'ken Prime were first mentioned in the comic book Star Wars 31, which was written by Jason Aaron and released on May 17, 2017.
